org.openarchitectureware.debug.processing.handlers
Class VariablesRuntimeHandler

java.lang.Object
  org.openarchitectureware.debug.processing.handlers.VariablesRuntimeHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable, IEventHandler, IRuntimeHandler
public class VariablesRuntimeHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRuntimeHandler, IEventHandler, java.lang.Runnable

This class handles the communication of variable names and values with the debug server.
It caches variable values with it's id and handles also cleanup of this cache if values are no longer used.

Author:
Clemens Kadura (zAJKa)
